<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %> – Kishore Orthopedic Centre</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero__inner">
        <div class="hero__content">
          <span class="badge">Trusted Orthopedic Care Since 2005</span>
          <h1>Your Path to <span class="text-accent">Pain-Free</span> Living Starts Here</h1>
          <p>Expert orthopedic care delivered with compassion. From sports injuries to joint replacements, we help you move better and live fuller.</p>
          <div class="hero__actions">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Contact Clinic</a>
            <a href="https://wa.me/917093571238" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">WhatsApp Inquiry</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero__trust">
            <div class="trust-item">
              <strong>10,000+</strong>
              <span>Patients Treated</span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-divider"></div>
            <div class="trust-item">
              <strong>20+</strong>
              <span>Years Experience</span>
            </div>
            <div class="trust-divider"></div>
            <div class="trust-item">
              <strong>98%</strong>
              <span>Success Rate</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__visual">
          <div class="hero__doctor-wrap">
            <img src="/images/doctor-kishore.png" alt="Dr. M. Kishore Kumar – Orthopedic Surgeon" class="hero__doctor-img" />
            <div class="hero__doctor-badge">
              <div class="hero__doctor-badge-content">
                <strong>Dr. M. Kishore Kumar</strong>
                <span>MS · DNB · MCH · FISS (Spine)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero__stat-card hero__stat-card--1">
              <span class="stat-num">24/7</span>
              <span class="stat-label">Emergency Care</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services Overview -->
    <section class="section services">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">What We Treat</span>
          <h2>Comprehensive Orthopedic Services</h2>
          <p>From acute injuries to chronic conditions, we provide personalised care using the latest techniques and technology.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-3">
          <div class="service-card card-hover">
            <div class="service-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/joint-replacement.jpg" alt="Joint Replacement" class="service-img" />
            </div>
            <div class="service-body">
              <h3>Joint Replacement</h3>
              <p>Advanced knee, hip and shoulder replacement surgeries with minimally invasive techniques for faster recovery.</p>
              <a href="/treatments" class="card-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card card-hover">
            <div class="service-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/arthroscopy.jpg" alt="Arthroscopy" class="service-img" />
            </div>
            <div class="service-body">
              <h3>Arthroscopy</h3>
              <p>Minimally invasive keyhole surgery for knee, shoulder and hip joints with smaller incisions and faster recovery.</p>
              <a href="/treatments" class="card-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card card-hover">
            <div class="service-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/spine.jpg" alt="Spine Care" class="service-img" />
            </div>
            <div class="service-body">
              <h3>Spine Care</h3>
              <p>Comprehensive treatment for back pain, disc problems, scoliosis and spinal deformities using advanced surgical options.</p>
              <a href="/treatments" class="card-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card card-hover">
            <div class="service-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/physiotherapy.jpg" alt="Physiotherapy" class="service-img" />
            </div>
            <div class="service-body">
              <h3>Physiotherapy & Rehab</h3>
              <p>Expert rehabilitation programmes to restore movement, reduce pain and prevent re-injury after surgery or trauma.</p>
              <a href="/treatments" class="card-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card card-hover">
            <div class="service-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/ilizarov.jpg" alt="Limb Reconstruction" class="service-img" />
            </div>
            <div class="service-body">
              <h3>Limb Reconstruction</h3>
              <p>Ilizarov technique for limb lengthening, deformity correction and bone reconstruction — fellowship trained in Russia.</p>
              <a href="/treatments" class="card-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-card card-hover">
            <div class="service-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/flap-coverage.jpg" alt="Trauma & Fracture Care" class="service-img" />
            </div>
            <div class="service-body">
              <h3>Trauma & Fracture Care</h3>
              <p>Prompt management of fractures, dislocations and complex trauma using modern fixation and wound coverage techniques.</p>
              <a href="/treatments" class="card-link">Learn more →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Choose Us -->
    <section class="section section-alt why-us">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="why-us__inner">
          <div class="why-us__content">
            <span class="section-tag">Why Choose Us</span>
            <h2>Care That Goes Beyond Treatment</h2>
            <p>We believe orthopedic care is about more than fixing bones — it's about restoring the quality of life for every patient and their family.</p>
            <ul class="why-list">
              <li>
                <div class="why-icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>International Fellowship Training</strong>
                  <p>Our surgeon is fellowship-trained in Switzerland and Russia, bringing world-class expertise to Vijayawada.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="why-icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>State-of-the-Art Facility</strong>
                  <p>Equipped with the latest imaging, surgical and rehabilitation equipment for the best outcomes.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="why-icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Patient-First Approach</strong>
                  <p>Every treatment plan is tailored to the individual — your goals, your timeline, your life.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="why-icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Affordable, Accessible Care</strong>
                  <p>Quality orthopedic care should be within reach for everyone in our community.</p>
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">Learn About Us</a>
          </div>
          <div class="why-us__visual">
            <div class="why-us__highlight-card">
              <img src="/images/kishore-russia.png" alt="Dr. M. Kishore Kumar — Ilizarov Fellowship, Kurgan Russia" class="why-us__highlight-img" />
              <div class="why-us__highlight-caption">
                <strong>Dr. M. Kishore Kumar</strong>
                <span>Fellowship Certificate — Russian Ilizarov Scientific Center, Kurgan, Russia</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Testimonials -->
    <section class="section testimonials">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Patient Stories</span>
          <h2>Words From Our Patients</h2>
          <p>Real experiences from the patients we have had the privilege to treat.</p>
        </div>

        <% if (testimonials && testimonials.length > 0) { %>
        <div class="testimonial-carousel" id="testimonialCarousel">
          <div class="carousel-track-wrapper">
            <div class="carousel-track">
              <% testimonials.forEach(function(fb) {
                   var initials = fb.patientName.split(' ').map(function(w){return w[0]||'';}).join('').toUpperCase().slice(0,2);
                   var filled = '★'.repeat(fb.rating);
                   var empty  = '☆'.repeat(5 - fb.rating);
              %>
              <div class="testimonial-card">
                <div class="tc-stars">
                  <span class="tc-stars__filled"><%= filled %></span><span class="tc-stars__empty"><%= empty %></span>
                </div>
                <p class="tc-message">"<%= fb.message %>"</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                  <div class="author-avatar"><%= initials %></div>
                  <div>
                    <strong><%= fb.patientName %></strong>
                    <span><%= fb.treatment %></span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <% if (fb.hospitalReply) { %>
                <div class="hospital-reply">
                  <span class="hospital-reply__label">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="12" height="12"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg>
                    Hospital Reply
                  </span>
                  <p><%= fb.hospitalReply %></p>
                </div>
                <% } %>
              </div>
              <% }); %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-controls">
            <button class="carousel-prev" aria-label="Previous slide">&#8249;</button>
            <div class="carousel-dots"></div>
            <button class="carousel-next" aria-label="Next slide">&#8250;</button>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% } else { %>
        <div class="grid grid-3">
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="tc-stars"><span class="tc-stars__filled">★★★★★</span></div>
            <p class="tc-message">"After my knee replacement at Kishore Orthopedic Centre, I'm back to playing cricket with my grandchildren. The care was exceptional and the team truly felt like family."</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="author-avatar">RK</div>
              <div><strong>Ramesh Kumar</strong><span>Knee Replacement Patient</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card testimonial-card--featured">
            <div class="tc-stars"><span class="tc-stars__filled">★★★★★</span></div>
            <p class="tc-message">"I came in with a severe sports injury and was back on the field in 3 months. Dr. Kishore and his team were incredibly supportive throughout my recovery journey."</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="author-avatar">PS</div>
              <div><strong>Priya Sharma</strong><span>Sports Injury Patient</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="tc-stars"><span class="tc-stars__filled">★★★★★</span></div>
            <p class="tc-message">"The physiotherapy programme here is outstanding. My back pain of 5 years is finally gone. Highly recommend Kishore Orthopedic Centre to everyone in Vijayawada."</p>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <div class="author-avatar">AV</div>
              <div><strong>Anil Varma</strong><span>Spine Care Patient</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="testimonials-cta">
          <a href="/feedback" class="btn btn-outline">Share Your Experience →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="section cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-box">
          <div class="cta-content">
            <h2>Ready to Take the First Step?</h2>
            <p>Contact our clinic today and let Dr. Kishore Kumar create a personalised treatment plan just for you.</p>
            <div class="cta-actions">
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-white btn-lg">Contact Clinic</a>
              <a href="https://wa.me/917093571238" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-outline-white btn-lg">WhatsApp Inquiry</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-info">
            <div class="cta-info-item">
              <span class="cta-info-icon">📞</span>
              <div>
                <strong>+91 70935 71238</strong>
                <span>Available 24/7 for Emergencies</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cta-info-item">
              <span class="cta-info-icon">📍</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Old Checkpost, Vijayawada</strong>
                <span>Sri Devi Apartments, Yalamalakuduru Lakulu Road</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
